{"tid":2200636,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"母發病攜子全民檢測 恐播毒  餐廳侍應中招 逾10同事拉隊驗疫","createTime":"2020-09-13T06:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T06:27:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6607745fefecc91d5e9e4789c5e88bfaeb5baa18","tid":2200636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/JXAJZZVHY5BPHAH5DQSJERPEBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FJXAJZZVHY5BPHAH5DQSJERPEBM%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513f4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=5c196c35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FJXAJZZVHY5BPHAH5DQSJERPEBM%2F&h=0b559dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/JXAJZZVHY5BPHAH5DQSJERPEBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n母發病攜子全民檢測 恐播毒 <br />\n餐廳侍應中招 逾10同事拉隊驗疫<br />\n<br />\n【疫情反覆】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：雙親染疫亡葬禮從簡 孝女留憾<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】數以億元計公帑的普及社區檢測計劃，推行至昨天12日，有166.6萬人次完成檢測，當中有32.1萬人未經預約，不僅違背政府曾聲稱防止人群聚集的承諾，更有確診個案證明，計劃被高危者濫用。一個油塘家庭群組，61歲女子有病徵仍做全民檢測；另一確診者的十多名同事亦拉隊參加檢測，所謂「為己為人」的檢測計劃，已淪為累己累人的播毒途徑。<br />\n<br />\n本港昨日新增13宗確診個案，本地個案佔九宗，另有十多宗初步確診個案。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：再有兩抵港菲傭確診  累計16人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nsbvVotIruCzfqX30_Fio-HDJqo=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGM5VSTRXJBJTHSVJ2PECKBBBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnsbvVotIruCzfqX30_Fio-HDJqo%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGM5VSTRXJBJTHSVJ2PECKBBBY.jpg&h=9de6cff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■油塘一家四口確診，其中61歲女子發病時仍到鯉魚門體育館參與全民檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一家四口全確診<br />\n<br />\n67歲男子在9月4日已病發，懷疑傳染了其他家人，但他延至9月9日才到聯合醫院急症室求醫並留下樣本。同一日，已發病的61歲女子亦與32歲男子一起到鯉魚門體育館參與全民檢測。<br />\n<br />\n9月10日67歲男子初步確診，中。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一位第4927號30歲女子，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nL&rsquo;Atlantis會停業14日，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運輸署職員中招<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷則認為，確診患者的緊密接觸者可能已有病徵而自己不察覺，防護中心應按既定程序向他們派發樣本瓶，任由接觸者到不同檢測中心採樣會交叉感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n曾又指，油塘家庭群組個案參。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其他個案包括第4936號51歲女子，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-Xz2JoW8eAKkEKMGlM1haILZjAA=/404x373/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QLY6BEXJAFGS5CFUGEGWY56LFA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-Xz2JoW8eAKkEKMGlM1haILZjAA%3D%2F404x373%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQLY6BEXJAFGS5CFUGEGWY56LFA.gif&h=9488abb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"183bf679849ae7c8b7d21bb29ef5503a55448852","tid":2200636,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"又係人工播毒推檢測"}]}